          "type": "calculation",
          "score": 10,
          "content": "设 $y=y(x)$ 由方程 $e^y+xy=e$ 确定，求 $y'(0)$。",
          "options": {},
          "answer": "$-\\frac{1}{e}$",
          "solution": "当 $x=0$ 时 $e^y=e\\Rightarrow y(0)=1$。方程两边对 $x$ 求导：$e^y y'+y+xy'=0$，代入 $x=0,y=1$ 得 $e\\cdot y'(0)+1=0$，故 $y'(0)=-\\frac{1}{e}$。",
          "analysis": "隐函数求导，注意代入初值。",
          "knowledge_points": [
            "kp-2-2-4"
          ],
          "difficulty": 3,
          "tags": [
            "隐函数求导"
          ]
